name: LAYA
description:
This song was recorded alongside the piece 'WATCH OUT.' Laya is a term in Filipino language which means 'Freedom.' To make music and art for me, is to release from the world that tries to put us in a box and restrict us from the things we never thought we could do as human beings. LAYA.
The song will be airdropped to 'WATCH OUT' collectors as well!!

two birds in one stone!!!
